---
import "../global.css";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import miika from "./miika.jpg";
import github from "/src/pages/github.svg";
import linkedin from "/src/pages/linkedin.svg";
import world from "/src/pages/world.svg";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Portfolio site of software engineer Miika Leinonen"
    />
    <title>Miika Leinonen</title>
  </head>
  <body class="font-mono bg-gray-50 w-full">
    <main>
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section
        class="max-w-2xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] items-center justify-between px-4 mt-16 mb-12"
      >
        <div class="row-2 sm:row-1 justify-self-center sm:justify-self-start">
          <h1 class="font-sans text-4xl font-medium my-2">Miika Leinonen</h1>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-center justify-center sm:justify-start">
            <a href="https://github.com/miikalei">
              <Image alt="Github logo" src={github} width="30" /></a
            >
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/miikaleinonen/">
              <Image alt="Linkedin logo" src={linkedin} width="30" />
            </a>
            <a href="/">
              <Image alt="Link to personal website" src={world} width="30" />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <Image
          class="justify-self-center sm:justify-self-end"
          style={{
            clipPath: "circle()",
          }}
          src={miika}
          alt="Image of a handsome young pro, battle bruised but still full of young energy"
          width={200}
        />
      </section>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 my-16">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Hello, My name is Miika. I am a professional software engineer, based
          in Helsinki, Finland. I am serious about honing my craft, and I take
          pride in my producing code that is as stable, performant and secure as
          possible. Welcome to my portfolio page.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Projects Section -->
      <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 my-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Stuff I have built</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold my-4">Upright</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              <a href="https://www.uprightproject.com/">Upright</a> is a company
              that develops a macroeconomic model for a holistic view on impact footprints
              of products, companies and funds. I joined them in the year 2021, and
              have been since focusing on the internal and external web app functionality
              to handle the large amount of data produced. Visit the <a
                href="https://uprightplatform.com/">Upright platform</a
              > to see the results!
            </p>
          </li>

          <li>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold my-4">MLox interpreter</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              In order to follow the excellent book <a
                href="https://craftinginterpreters.com/"
                >Crafting interpreters</a
              > by Robert Nystrom, I implemented my own mod of the language built
              in the book. My (toy) language is called mlox, and <a href="/mlox"
                >you can try it in the browser</a
              >. The interpreter is written in Typescript, and <a
                href="https://github.com/miikalei/mlox"
                >its source is available on GitHub.</a
              >
            </p>
          </li>

          <li>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold my-4">This website</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              The website you are viewing right now is built with Astro and
              served with GitHub pages. It utilizes React components and
              Tailwind. Check out the source on <a
                href="https://github.com/miikalei/miikalei.github.io">GitHub</a
              >.
            </p>
          </li>

          <li>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold my-4">Miscellaneous exercises</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              I like solving simple structured programming puzzles for the easy
              comparisons to alternative solutions. Check out my <a
                href="https://github.com/miikalei/aoc"
                >Advent of Code solutions (Rust)</a
              > and <a href="https://github.com/miikalei/project-euler"
                >Project Euler solutions (Python)</a
              >. I also play CTFs at <a href="https://overthewire.org"
                >Overthewire.org</a
              >.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Education -->
      <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 my-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Education</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 my-1">
          Master of Science and Bachelor of Science at Aalto University, 300
          ETCS, 2015-2021. Graduated with honors, with GPA 4.95 / 5.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 my-1">
          Main focus of my studies was on pure mathematics, with secondary focus
          on computer science, graphics and machine learning.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 my-1">
          My master's thesis, <a
            href="https://aaltodoc.aalto.fi/items/16c62b40-2245-4875-a6e8-33661bed8393"
            >Federated Multi-task Learning over Networked Data</a
          >, is freely available for reading. My bachelor's thesis, <a
            href="https://aaltodoc.aalto.fi/items/5422ef14-df68-415b-bb6a-ab8d008c7849"
            >Quaternion algebras and well-rounded lattices</a
          >, is available offline in the Aalto University library.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Technologies -->
      <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 my-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Technologies I've used</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Languages</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>
                <strong>Typescript</strong> – Most professional experience. Frontend,
                backend and scripting
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Python</strong> – Mainly for data analysis and scripting
              </li>
              <li><strong>C/C++</strong> – Graphics and big math</li>
              <li><strong>Rust</strong> – Hobbyist, exercises</li>
              <li><strong>Scala</strong> – University courses only</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Backend & DevOps</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>PostgreSQL</li>
              <li>Node.js</li>
              <li>Docker</li>
              <li>Docker swarm</li>
              <li>AWS</li>
              <li>Linux</li>
              <li>Opentelemetry</li>
              <li>Jaeger</li>
              <li>Prometheus</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Frontend</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>React</li>
              <li>HTML/CSS</li>
              <li>Astro</li>
              <li>TailwindCSS</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Data analysis & ML</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>Python notebooks</li>
              <li>Numpy + Scipy</li>
              <li>Pytorch</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer
    class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 w-full py-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center"
  >
    <p>Miika Leinonen, 2025</p>
    <p>
      Check out the website <a
        href="https://github.com/miikalei/miikalei.github.io">source</a
      >
    </p>
  </footer>
</html>
